summary: This is an internal FBI email distributing the Director's morning news briefing for February 25, 2019. It contains standard administrative information about distribution, copyright, and contact procedures, but no substantive content about the Epstein case is provided in this header text.
keyFacts: Document is an internal FBI email distributing the Director's AM News Briefing dated February 25, 2019.

The attached briefing document (FBIDirBriefing190225.doc) is referenced but its content is not included in this text.
